nodes.text: Lanoree Brock's father was a male Human and the Je'daii Temple Master overseeing Bodhi, the Temple of Arts, for the Je'daii Order on Tython at the height of the Infinite Empire's reign. Brock and his wife were the parents of Lanoree Brock, a Je'daii Ranger, and Dalien Brock the founder of the Stargazers.
